some further questions.

464
00:40:59,915 --> 00:41:03,377
If you say so, I'm happy to help.

465
00:41:04,128 --> 00:41:05,713
Thank you.

466
00:41:07,006 --> 00:41:08,757
First of all,

467
00:41:09,633 --> 00:41:13,345
