in orphanages, like me.

527
00:45:58,755 --> 00:46:00,007
The killer's after…

528
00:46:02,801 --> 00:46:04,428
the neuro chips.

529
00:46:07,890 --> 00:46:11,602
Disable a security camera
to strip a wallet?

530
00:46:11,685 --> 00:46:14,646
