<i>Let the heat of the sunlight</i>

915
01:14:00,602 --> 01:14:04,398
<i>Warm up the rock plenty</i>

916
01:14:05,899 --> 01:14:11,447
<i>When I was sitting down</i>
<i>Next to the little rock</i>

917
01:14:12,072 --> 01:14:17,369
<i>Funny thing is I became a little rock too</i>

918
01:14:17,453 --> 01:14:23,333
<i>And my heart got warm inside bit by bit</i>

919
01:14:24,042 --> 01:14:29,214
<i>It made me so happy</i>
<i>That I wanted to sing out loud</i>

920
